Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:04.47,Chiha-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:06.15,Chiha-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That should be all of the large boxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:08.96,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go say "goodbye" to the landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:09.57,Chiha-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:14.15,shirt,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Team Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:22.37,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The next time we meet will \Nbe at the nationals!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:25.21,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:28.43,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me become a Class A player!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:29.97,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You won't beat me next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:30.83,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:33.19,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become a Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:34.43,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:43.77,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Guess this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:45.68,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:47.39,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet again when we \Nbecome Class A players!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:51.16,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:24.73,Chiha-title,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:34.13,Chiha-ep-title-poem,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,800)}A Whirlwind \Nof Flower \NPetals \NDescends
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:34.02,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,800)}Verse 4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:37.57,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, this is our stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:53.31,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Were you daydreaming or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.82,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you been in touch with Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:00.70,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:03.12,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:09.15,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Arata must be incredibly strong now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.71,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we'll see him at this \Nyear's Omi Jingu tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.78,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:18.34,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You want to play against Arata \Nin the national tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:19.59,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.55,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What class are you right now, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:26.26,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I made Class B in the \Ntournament during spring break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:30.10,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it'll take you another \Nthree years to make Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.39,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just stick with track?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.48,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of hanging around in \NClass B for three more years...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.40,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:43.68,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You're just as violent \Nas you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:45.48,Chiha-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.30,Chiha-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:51.75,Chiha-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I came all the way here \Nto show you my uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:52.58,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:54.46,ta-kun,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}She calls him Ta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.46,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.56,Chiha-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:01.19,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:06.72,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If I win the tournament on \NSunday and make Class A,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:09.25,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,you have to help me \Nstart a karuta club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.27,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.76,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how hard it \Nis to make Class A in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:15.83,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.48,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.48,Chiha-overlap,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, who is she, Ta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.25,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:28.24,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him pay for getting \Nhimself a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.10,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to tell somebody!  Anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.75,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She was calling Taichi "Ta-kun"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:37.25,phone,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya Arata - Home in Fukui
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:45.80,phone2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya Arata - Home in Fukui
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.64,bunkyo,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,200)}Bunkyo City\NOtsuka Karuta Memorial Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.18,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,And here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:00.04,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forget.{Orig: I couldn't stop thinking about what she said.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.30,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Eye!  Eye!  Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:11.96,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:14.16,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Harada, I can't believe \Nyou actually recognized me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:16.30,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.32,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Are your armpits and \Npubes all bushy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:21.61,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,But not as bushy as your eyebrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:23.67,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.00,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Could you be quiet while \Nthey're memorizing the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:27.25,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.73,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,You already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.22,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  You're here to \Ncheer for Chihaya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.31,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:41.25,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Looks pretty tense in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:45.39,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,They have to win if they want \Nto advance to the next class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.80,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's especially hard \Non the Class B players.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:50.52,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,There are many strong players\N who spend years in Class B
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:53.78,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,because they can't rack up enough wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.73,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's trying as hard as they \Ncan to reach the next level.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:06:00.02,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If I win the tournament \Nand make Class A,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.92,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,you have to help me \Nstart a karuta club!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:05.81,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna take you a \Nwhile to make Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:17.82,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows, I heard that you're in the \Nsame high school as Chihaya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:19.03,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.74,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a karuta club, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:24.86,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,You should come practice \Nwith the Shiranami Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:25.90,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.76,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm thinking about \Njoining the soccer team.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:30.91,quiet,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Please be quiet\N during matches
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:30.91,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:33.81,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to turn into \Na two-timing bastard
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:35.04,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,or you'll never become a Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:39.16,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.54,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's not my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:45.74,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:49.01,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I played karuta in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.55,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a small club, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:55.61,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced and became \Nbetter little by little,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.56,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,but I always knew, deep down,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:05.04,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,that I could spend my\N entire youth on karuta
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.99,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,without ever becoming \Nbetter than Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:15.72,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Naniwa Bay, now the flower \Nblooms, but for winter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:16.68,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,They're starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:23.37,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, \Nnow the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:31.21,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, \Nnow the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.36,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,So spring ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.53,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:39.61,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she yelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.54,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Did you teach her to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:43.47,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Not under normal circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:46.36,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,but I gave her a few tips since \Nshe wanted to win so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:51.20,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,If someone challenges her, \Nshe's supposed to complain
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:54.36,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,loud enough that everyone in the room can hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:58.29,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The hazy early morning light comes not from the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:58.29,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,The point is to overwhelm her opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:00.04,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Is she really so obsessed with winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:05.79,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,When Chihaya-chan entered middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:23.85,Chiha-flashback,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Why track?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.72,Chiha-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,There a reason for choosing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.86,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You know how you're supposed to start \Nrunning when you hear the starter pistol fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.59,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It reminds me of karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:37.37,Chiha-flashback,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.87,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll also help me get in shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.25,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is for karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:50.10,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,"Spend your entire youth \Nwithout becoming stronger"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:52.76,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.33,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,hold that thought for now.
