Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:10.15,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:13.69,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for raising my \Nvoice during the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:24.46,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:25.46,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,An okay sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.29,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,That's the chocolate sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.77,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:30.49,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows, run down to \Nthe convenience store
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:31.39,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and buy some chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:32.46,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.72,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!  Go!
