Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.68,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.38,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,"Convenience" my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.73,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other shops around here?
