Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:06.40,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:13.33,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:14.99,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Savor them, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:17.45,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat three of them at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.26,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,These are good, Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:20.89,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,So many different flavors!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.52,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta tournaments are \Nlong and grueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:28.78,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,You have to memorize the \Npositions of fifty cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:30.53,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,then forget them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:32.36,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Memorize, then forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:36.98,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,The longest tournaments require \Nyou to play seven matches,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:39.03,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,from morning till night,\N before there can be a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.87,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Your brain will burn through \Nthe sugar in your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.67,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,and you can lose up to three kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:48.17,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,So players eat chocolate \Nto recharge themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:50.10,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Chihaya-chan?
