Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.58,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass. \N I can't do anything if I'm inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:05.41,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll join you outside.
