Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.58,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,However, he will be a formidable foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:16.17,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,He has the ability, but he's been \Nstuck in Class B for three years.
